{"tid":2187442,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)THE ROCK系列","createTime":"2020-09-03T15:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T18:49:01.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dc3620accf7b19f70b0cff25ea7fe23773af53d4","tid":2187442,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:20:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=8720e059\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=111fadc0\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=7c24b65d\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/87/The_Rundown_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F87%2FThe_Rundown_poster.jpg&h=1b49fd23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.comingsoon.net/assets/uploads/2017/04/rampageheader3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.comingsoon.net%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Frampageheader3.jpg&h=e7284094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.賞金獵人貝克（巨石強森）為他的僱主比利去巴西熱帶雨林尋找叛逆離家的兒子特拉維斯（西恩&middot;威廉&middot;史考特），貝克租用了戴克林的飛機和汽車來到巴西熱帶雨林，卻發現康奈紐斯&middot;伯納德&middot;哈奇（克里斯多夫&middot;華肯）非法奴役當地的印第安人為他挖礦淘金。特拉維斯曾經在美國史丹福大學讀書，中途輟學來到這裡尋找印第安文化中遺失的寶物「嘎圖」（一尊神像），他和印地安女孩瑪麗&middot;安娜（羅莎里奧&middot;道森）是好友，兩人都對嘎圖有著強烈的好奇心，兩人都懂葡萄牙語<br />\n<br />\n2.人類在1993年開發出基因編輯技術CRISPR，開始用於治療致命疾病方面，但因不法分子濫用此技術，因此在2016年被美國情報體系勒令禁止所有相關研究。如今，不法企業「基因能源公司」（Energyne）仍然秘密將技術用於基因工程方面，在大氣層外的空間站「雅典娜一號」（Athena-1）裡著手「毀滅計劃」（Project Rampage）。但一隻實驗老鼠服用公司開發出的病原體後，突變成一隻攻擊性極強的變種老鼠而殺死所有研究員。空間站僅倖存的研究員凱莉&middot;艾特金斯將三個病原體樣本帶回逃生艙後撤離出去，但進入大氣層期間因窗戶破損而死於逃生艙燃盡<br />\n<br />\n11 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=62f1ad55\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=d4c8d7e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d1d0451b53327d6a16beab5d831c28051fc297","tid":2187442,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda7725c426760ad7db5b4f1ef85970851eb9f6b","tid":2187442,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T16:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c323cbd01b23d3d0b6622efd1988a8fdd21e0d49","tid":2187442,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed99da6e4f1712c068582440b4f534893c0ca94","tid":2187442,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T18:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}